OL,3,CUkraine: Scottish driver says 'there
OL,4,Cso much less' aid for war-torn nation
OL,6,FA man from south-west who is on his
OL,7,Ffourth trip delivering humanitarian
OL,8,Fsupplies to people in Ukraine says the
OL,9,Famount of aid being delivered there
OL,10,Fhas massively reduced, as the war
OL,11,Fenters its third calendar year.
OL,13,FIain Gordon, who is from spoke to ITV
OL,14,FNews from Kharkiv, less than thirty
OL,15,Fmiles from the Russian border. The
OL,16,Fvolunteer driver has been handing out
OL,17,Fdonations to community organisations
OL,18,Fand homes housing orphaned children in
OL,19,Fand around the city.
