OL,6,F"Every fourth or fifth house has been
OL,7,Fdestroyed," he said. "But these people
OL,8,Fare still living here in amongst this
OL,9,Fdestruction."
OL,11,FOn previous trips Iain has collected
OL,12,Faid from across But this time round,
OL,13,Fhe says, everything has been donated
OL,14,Fby people, businesses, schools, and
OL,15,Fthe football club in his home town.
