OL,6,F"I couldn't have done this trip
OL,7,Fwithout the people of Stranraer.
OL,8,FEverything I had in that minibus was
OL,9,Fdonated by the wonderful people of my
OL,10,Fcommunity, Stranraer and the outlying
OL,11,Farea," he said.
OL,13,F"So from me, a great big thank you,
OL,14,Fbut mostly from the people here that
OL,15,Fhave been receiving this aid. Thank
OL,16,Fyou so very, very much, for your help,
OL,17,Fand your kindness."
