OL,3,CUkraine: Scottish driver says 'there
OL,4,Cso much less' aid for war-torn nation
OL,6,FIain's journey took him over two
OL,7,Fthousand miles from south-western
OL,8,Fcoast to the frontlines near Kharkiv,
OL,9,Fpassing shattered buildings as he
OL,10,Fcarried toys, clothes, and electric
OL,11,Fwheelchairs in the back of a minibus,
OL,12,Fdecked out with the names of
OL,13,Fcontributors and Scottish flags.
OL,15,FBut since his first trip to the
OL,16,Fbeleaguered nation shortly after the
OL,17,F2022 invasion, Iain said he'd seen a
OL,18,Flarge reduction in the amount of aid
OL,19,Fvehicles he'd seen on the roads.
OL,20,F"Things have changed," he said.
