OL,3,CUkraine: Scottish driver says 'there
OL,4,Cso much less' aid for war-torn nation
OL,6,F"There's so much less aid arriving
OL,7,Fhere. Even on the drive out from the
OL,8,FUK, I didn't see another single
OL,9,Fhumanitarian aid vehicle.
OL,11,F"I was the only one I could see in the
OL,12,Froad the whole way."JThere are fears
OL,13,Fthat the public is growing weary of
OL,14,Fthe conflict in the West, with Polish
OL,15,FPresident Donald Tusk condemning
OL,16,Fapathy towards the situation as
OL,17,F"completely unacceptable" in December.
