OL,6,FSupport for Ukraine is also becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly strained in the , where
OL,8,FRepublican Congressmen are attempting
OL,9,Fto block the Biden administration from
OL,10,Fsending military and humanitarian aid
OL,11,Fto the country worth around $60
OL,12,Fbillion.
OL,14,FThe UK has pledged #2.5 million worth
OL,15,Fof military aid to Ukraine over 2024,
OL,16,Fwith the Prime Minister telling
OL,17,FUkrainian President Zelenskyy that
OL,18,Fsupport from the UK "wasn't going
OL,19,Fanywhere."
